headline: Reflecting On Transportation and Logistics Stocks’ Q3 Earnings: CSX (NASDAQ:CSX)
summary: As the Q3 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the transportation and logistics industry, including CSX (NASDAQ:CSX) and its peers.
